            </div>
            <div class="mt-3 flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-terminal-green font-bold">Result:</span>
              <span class="text-terminal-text">Claude creates files like HUMAN-CONTENT-NEEDED.md, HUMAN-CREDENTIALS.md - clean handoff points.</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Prompt 5: RALPH Loop -->
